      <h2>What You'll Need</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>A VPS running Ubuntu 22.04+ or Debian 12+ (providers like Hetzner, DigitalOcean, Linode all work)</li>
        <li>At least 1 GB RAM and 10 GB storage</li>
        <li>SSH access to your server</li>
        <li>A domain name (optional but recommended)</li>
        <li>An Anthropic API key</li>
      </ul>

